Privacy Policy for MferSafe Lite

Last updated: 2023

MferSafe Lite ("we", "us", "our") values the privacy of our users. This Privacy Policy outlines how we handle and protect the personal information of users who download and use MferSafe Lite.

By downloading and using MferSafe Lite, you agree to the collection and use of your information as described in this Privacy Policy.

Information Collection and Use
MferSafe Lite is designed to provide a secure browsing experience. We do not collect or store any personal or sensitive user data while you use the extension.

Log Data
MferSafe Lite does not collect any log data or information related to your browsing activities.

Cookies
MferSafe Lite does not use cookies to track user activities or store any user information.

Security
The security of your personal information is important to us. While we do not collect personal or sensitive user data, we are committed to using commercially acceptable means to protect any information that may be shared with us.

Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page. You are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes. Changes to this Privacy Policy are effective when they are posted on this page.

By using MferSafe Lite, you consent to our Privacy Policy.
